      <title>hexo和next主题配置</title>
      <link href="/2019/09/06/hexo%E5%92%8Cnext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
      <url>/2019/09/06/hexo%E5%92%8Cnext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>上一篇文章中主要讲述了用<a href="[https://youngmyone.github.io/2019/09/05/hexo-github%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/](https://youngmyone.github.io/2019/09/05/hexo-github搭建个人博客/)">hexo和github搭建免费博客</a>，但是只是完成了博客的基本雏形。这篇文章则是对hexo进行一些配置，使其更加个性化。</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="config-yml文件配置"><a href="#config-yml文件配置" class="headerlink" title="_config.yml文件配置"></a>_config.yml文件配置</h1><p>首先在你放置代码的根目录下找到_config.yml文件。这个文件主要用于配置网站的相关信息。</p><h2 id="站点配置"><a href="#站点配置" class="headerlink" title="站点配置"></a>站点配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Site</span><br><span class="line">title: youngmyone&apos;s blogs// 网站标题</span><br><span class="line">subtitle: 居于扁舟，行于江湖，来来去去// 副标题</span><br><span class="line">description:// 网站描述</span><br><span class="line">keywords:</span><br><span class="line">author: youngmyone// 作者</span><br><span class="line">language: zh-CN// 网站使用语言</span><br><span class="line">timezone:// 时区，默认使用电脑时区</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="URL配置"><a href="#URL配置" class="headerlink" title="URL配置"></a>URL配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># URL</span><br><span class="line">## If your site is put in a subdirectory, set url as &apos;http://yoursite.com/child&apos; and root as &apos;/child/&apos;</span><br><span class="line">url: https://youngmyone.github.io</span><br><span class="line">root: /</span><br><span class="line">permalink: :year/:month/:day/:title/</span><br><span class="line">permalink_defaults:</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="主题配置"><a href="#主题配置" class="headerlink" title="主题配置"></a>主题配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: next// 默认是landscape</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Git部署配置"><a href="#Git部署配置" class="headerlink" title="Git部署配置"></a>Git部署配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: git@github.com:youngmyone/youngmyone.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>其他配置基本不用动，可根据自己的需要来进行修改。</p><hr><h1 id="next主题"><a href="#next主题" class="headerlink" title="next主题"></a>next主题</h1><h2 id="下载next主题"><a href="#下载next主题" class="headerlink" title="下载next主题"></a>下载next主题</h2><p>打开Git Bash，定位到你搭建博客的站点目录下，利用git命令将next主题下载下来。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ cd your-hexo-site</span><br><span class="line">$ git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成之后，你可以在themes文件夹下看到next主题文件夹。</p><p>如果想要启用主题，那么按照上面主题配置的方式即可。配置完成之后，最好使用hexo clean命令对缓存进行清除。</p><p>启用hexo服务：hexo s，在浏览器地址栏输入<a href="http://localhost:4000，查看主题是否启用成功。成功的话，如下图所示。" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000，查看主题是否启用成功。成功的话，如下图所示。</a></p><img src="/2019/09/06/hexo和next主题配置/next启用成功.png" title="next启用成功"><h2 id="next中-config-yml配置"><a href="#next中-config-yml配置" class="headerlink" title="next中_config.yml配置"></a>next中_config.yml配置</h2><p>在your_blog_site/themes/next中找到_config.yml文件。下面说的_config.yml文件都是指这里的文件。</p><h3 id="Schemes配置"><a href="#Schemes配置" class="headerlink" title="Schemes配置"></a>Schemes配置</h3><p>schemes包括4中不同的风格的主题样式。如果想要启用其中的一个，则直接将其前面的注释去掉，其他的scheme打上注释。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Schemes</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Muse</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Mist</span><br><span class="line">#scheme: Pisces</span><br><span class="line">scheme: Gemini</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="设置-头像"><a href="#设置-头像" class="headerlink" title="设置 头像"></a>设置 头像</h3><p>在_config.yml文件中找到avatar字段。</p><ol><li>url是设置头像的路径，可以将自己想要的头像放在your_hexo_site/themes/next/source/images文件夹中。</li><li>rounded是设置头像是否是圆形，默认是方形的。</li><li>rotated设置头像是否旋转，圆形头像下生效。</li></ol><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Sidebar Avatar</span><br><span class="line">avatar:</span><br><span class="line">  # In theme directory (source/images): /images/avatar.gif</span><br><span class="line">  # In site directory (source/uploads): /uploads/avatar.gif</span><br><span class="line">  # You can also use other linking images.</span><br><span class="line">  url: /images/avatar.jpg</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar would be dispalyed in circle.</span><br><span class="line">  rounded: false</span><br><span class="line">  # If true, the avatar would be rotated with the cursor.</span><br><span class="line">  rotated: false</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="menu设置"><a href="#menu设置" class="headerlink" title="menu设置"></a>menu设置</h3><p>刚开始next主题默认的菜单只有首页(home)和归档(archives)两个。如果需要添加菜单的话，则在_config.yml文件中找到menu字段。自己想要那个菜单就把那个菜单前的注释取消。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">menu:</span><br><span class="line">  home: / || home</span><br><span class="line">  #about: /about/ || user</span><br><span class="line">  tags: /tags/ || tags</span><br><span class="line">  categories: /categories/ || th</span><br><span class="line">  archives: /archives/ || archive</span><br><span class="line">  #schedule: /schedule/ || calendar</span><br><span class="line">  #sitemap: /sitemap.xml || sitemap</span><br><span class="line">  #commonweal: /404/ || heartbeat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="添加分类"><a href="#添加分类" class="headerlink" title="添加分类"></a>添加分类</h4><ol><li><p>新建一个分类页面：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在your_blog_site/source文件夹下出现了categories目录。</p></li><li><p>现在可以把_config.yml文件中menu字段categories的注释取消。</p></li><li><p>如果想把写的文章归类，那么可以在创建的文章title下面加上categories字段，next主题可以自动把文章归类。比如：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 新的文章名</span><br><span class="line">categories: 分类名</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h4 id="添加标签"><a href="#添加标签" class="headerlink" title="添加标签"></a>添加标签</h4><ol><li><p>新建标签页面</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>同样在your_blog_site/source文件夹下出现tags目录。</p></li><li><p>取消tags注释</p></li><li><p>如果想要文章自动地归类到相应的标签中，可以在新建的文章title下面添加tags字段。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">title: 新建的文章名</span><br><span class="line">tags:</span><br><span class="line">- 标签1</span><br><span class="line">- 标签2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="搜索功能"><a href="#搜索功能" class="headerlink" title="搜索功能"></a>搜索功能</h3><p>这里主要介绍本地搜索功能。</p><ol><li><p>首先需要安装插件：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在_config.yml文件中找到local_search字段，将enable改为true</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># Local Search</span><br><span class="line"># Dependencies: https://github.com/wzpan/hexo-generator-search</span><br><span class="line">local_search:</span><br><span class="line">  enable: true</span><br><span class="line">  # If auto, trigger search by changing input.</span><br><span class="line">  # If manual, trigger search by pressing enter key or search button.</span><br><span class="line">  trigger: auto</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="全文阅读"><a href="#全文阅读" class="headerlink" title="全文阅读"></a>全文阅读</h3><p>next主题默认首页显示每篇文章的全文，显然不太方便。我们可以在我们写的文章中添加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;!--more--&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样首页就不会显示全文，需要点击全文阅读才能访问整篇文章。</p><h3 id="站点访问统计"><a href="#站点访问统计" class="headerlink" title="站点访问统计"></a>站点访问统计</h3><p>在_config.yml中找到busuanzi_count字段，将enable改为true即可。本地访问的时候统计数会显得很大，但是将其部署到GitHub上时，该功能就能正常使用了。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
